\par 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Each time you freeze chicken, you sacrifice quality. If carefully handled, however, it is safe to defrost uncooked chicken and to freeze it again after cooking.  If frozen after cooking, do not thaw and freeze again.
