\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
_Keep food safety in mind as you work.  Keep perishable food, such as chicken, in the refrigerator except when you're working with it.  Prepare food in batches and have out only what you're using. When refrigerating foods, have them in small enough 
